This card cannot be Normal Summon or Set. This card cannot be Special Summoned except by Tributing 1 Levia-Dragon - Daedalus on your side of the field. Send Umi on your side of the field to the Graveyard to send all cards in both players'' hands and on the field to the Graveyard, except this card.
